data.description: Precious once story home set on wooded lot in established PearlandISD neighborhood! All sides brick, entry hall, formal dining, spacious family room with vaulted ceiling opens into the completely remodeled kitchen with updated cabinets, counters, appliances , light fixtures and more. All 3 bedrooms are a good size and offer nice closet space. Bathrooms have been updated as well with Other updates include all flooring, paint and more. Call today for your personal tour!
